Botswana                        1.22          1.947              1,600
Lesotho                         1.72          0.809                470
Malawi                          8.23          1.481                180
Mozambique                     15.36          1.229                 80
Namibia                         1.30          1.525              1,173
Swaziland                       0.76          0.685                900
Tanzania                       25.63          3.075                120
