<TEXT>
RIGHT-WING militants in Rostock yesterday threatened to continue their
attacks on asylum seekers and the police until the September 1 anniversary
of Nazi Germany's invasion of Poland 53 years ago, writes Leslie Colitt in
Berlin.
Rostock police said they were taking the warning seriously. The neo-Nazis
