Earnings per share increased to 4.9 cents (4.3 cents).
This brings the loss for the half year to CDollars 1.5m against Dollars
2.02m. Sales improved from CDollars 17.4m to CDollars 18.6m.
Losses per share came out at 5.6 cents (8.2 cents) and the interim dividend
is again 2.5 cents.
